flask_app/
│── app.py                  # Main Flask app
│── config.py               # Config settings (PostgreSQL, etc.)
│── models.py               # Database models (Drivers & Vehicles)
│── requirements.txt        # Dependencies
│── routes/
│    ├── __init__.py
│    ├── driver.py          # Driver-related routes
│    ├── vehicle.py         # Vehicle-related routes
│── templates/
│    ├── base.html
│    ├── index.html
│    ├── driver.html
│    ├── vehicle.html
│── static/
│    ├── css/
│    │    └── style.css
│    └── js/
